Predator/Otyebis Staff:




The immobile Predator was struck dead on with both missiles exploding into a 
fiery death.

"Blacknightmare is the winner!" the announcer's voice rang out, the crowd 
applauding Blacknightmare for a minute but then leaving to go watch to the 
other fights.

Several soldiers approached Blacknightmare as a maintenace crew began 
cleaning up the mess that was what was left of Predator's body.  "Follow us." 
the soldiers said, heading for the only exit out of the arena.
